Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.-90,0:00:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people seek\Nthe answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future--\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright, but I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really, really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really need\Neverything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.37,0:01:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.04,0:01:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! There's a flock of birds to starboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.38,0:01:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alrighty!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.78,0:01:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.32,0:01:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Grab!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a sec... Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.66,0:01:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.33,0:02:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.01,0:02:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A wind is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A strong wind is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like this ship hasn't\Nbeen moving at all for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.02,0:02:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.03,0:02:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...!\NWe've entered the Calm Belt!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Charm Belt?\N--What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.36,0:02:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm Belt! It's an area of sea\Nwhere nothing moves a muscle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Nami grew her muscles"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that? An earthquake?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earthquake? On the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.81,0:02:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, enough chit chat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:02:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fold the sails and start paddling now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put the ship back on its earlier path!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.65,0:03:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you panicking about?\NPaddling? This is a sailboat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right. Why're we taking\Nthe trouble to go back
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.56,0:03:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to where the Navy is waiting for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do what I say!\NWe're in big trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.50,0:03:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the sea is quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, fine! Then I'll\Nexplain it for you! Listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we rushed and ran away,\Nwe came further south than we planned!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then did we enter the Grand Line?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it was that easy, anyone could enter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.35,0:03:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look. The Grand Line is\Nrunning between two sea areas!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The area on both sides of\Nit is called the Calm Belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The reason is unknown but in these areas,\Nthere's no wind and no current.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're an area of sea with complete calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.64,0:03:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailboats run by catching winds,\Nso it's an extremely dangerous area,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,indeed, a fatal area, for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.64,0:04:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. At least that we're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Good, you got more than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what the geezer meant\Nwhen he said it was dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.98,0:04:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder there hasn't been any wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.65,0:04:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do anything\Nif the ship doesn't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.32,0:04:12.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can just wait until\Nthe wind starts blowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, once you're in\Nthis area, wind never blows
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter how long you wait!\NAnd, that's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's another reason that\Npeople call this area dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this area...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.34,0:04:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.01,0:04:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something is coming this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they are!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.69,0:04:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.30,0:04:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're huge!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:05:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Calm Belt is the\Nnest of the Sea Kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, the ones here are super huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.31,0:05:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're another reason why\Npeople can't cross the Calm Belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.65,0:05:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Miraculous Creature! Apis's Secret\Nand the Legendary Island"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're we gonna do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.99,0:05:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-For the time being, no one move.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll probably go back\Ninto the sea eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.33,0:05:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll paddle hard using our oars.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.67,0:05:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.34,0:05:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.34,0:05:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.61,0:05:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A frog is coming!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.18,0:05:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What?! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.68,0:05:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.63,0:06:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Your arm is stretching!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Do you have\Nthe power of a devil fruit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:11.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.31,0:06:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stretch your arm downwards again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.65,0:06:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.32,0:06:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.66,0:06:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apis!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.66,0:06:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.33,0:06:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did she just do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She pulled his nose hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a sec...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.01,0:06:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna sneeze!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.34,0:06:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.28,0:06:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a huge nose hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! We're going back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:07:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it some other way!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.63,0:07:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! I feel like we're flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.63,0:07:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are flying!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we're back\Nin the area we came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see any sign of the Navy, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.98,0:07:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh... I thought I was a goner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.32,0:07:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Good job!\N--Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Unfurl the sails!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our destination is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.66,0:07:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Warship Island!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.33,0:07:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we can see the fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.66,0:07:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apis, is it really around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.67,0:07:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.00,0:07:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Not sure"? You...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be close by.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure know your stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! It's a sailboat! It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.62,0:07:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now listen here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The word "huge" doesn't\Nbegin to describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, a super humongous sailboat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.46,0:08:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Warship Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's shaped like a warship,\Nso it's called Warship Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.96,0:08:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.64,0:08:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! That flag is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.88,0:08:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates!! Pirates have come!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.62,0:08:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.27,0:08:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi! I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.61,0:08:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apis...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.44,0:08:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you coming out\Nfrom the pirate ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.11,0:09:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.62,0:09:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a BBQ restaurant on this island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.12,0:09:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.62,0:09:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.96,0:09:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! They're pirates,\Nbut they're good ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.96,0:09:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Are there really good pirates?\N--Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.97,0:09:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you taken away by\Nthe Navy in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. But I escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And these guys, Luffy and\Nthe others, saved me. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.65,0:09:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you do, Apis?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.31,0:09:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know why, but the\NNavy was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.32,0:09:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should stay away from your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.45,0:09:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're still around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.99,0:09:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd like to help, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.66,0:09:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...they're pirates, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.33,0:09:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.33,0:09:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like she said, we're good pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.67,0:09:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:10:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Who's that?\N--Don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.68,0:10:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Bokuden!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.02,0:10:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for saving Apis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.69,0:10:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this? I'd like to throw\Na small welcome party for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.36,0:10:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your place a BBQ restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a BBQ restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Grandpa Bokuden's pork buns\Nare the best on the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, we'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.32,0:10:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.99,0:10:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.67,0:11:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eric!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.67,0:11:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been here all along...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that that girl\Ngot lost in the Calm Belt
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and wasn't going to come back alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.34,0:11:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be... That girl...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.36,0:11:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...back on Warship Island!\NCapture that girl, you bum!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.69,0:11:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then they escaped from the Calm Belt...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.16,0:12:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the preparations are finished.\NWait a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.99,0:12:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.99,0:12:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Smells good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... This is the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.46,0:12:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man, how long do we have to wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.67,0:12:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,maybe about 4-5 hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.01,0:12:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.01,0:12:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bokuden-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.11,0:12:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why is the Navy after Apis?\NDo you have any idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.35,0:12:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apis! Do you have any idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.02,0:12:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said there was a reason\Nbut you didn't want to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.69,0:12:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh that! I lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?\N--Then none at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.69,0:12:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None at all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, there's nothing on this island.\NNothing but an old legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.70,0:12:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Legend?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The residents of this island are said\Nto be descendants of Lost Island people
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:49.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who prospered but sank into the sea\Ntens of thousands of years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.31,0:12:53.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On Lost Island, there lived\Ndragons called Millennial Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.31,0:12:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bones of those dragons\Nare called Dragonite...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.32,0:13:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and it's said to be\Nan elixir of immortality.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.15,0:13:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But a legend like that is no reason\Nfor the Navy to get involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Why is the Navy doing\Nthis in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.99,0:13:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the thing I don't get.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't this legend hold some\Nsort of clue or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To begin with, the first king
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.33,0:13:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Here we go again...\N--of Lost Island was Iscardunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, King PokePortes had three children.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.01,0:13:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The oldest son was BokeHontas,\Nthe second son was BokeBonboko, and
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--the third son was BokeBokepon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Shhh!\N--the third son was BokeBokepon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.68,0:13:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Shhh!\N--One day, the king said to these three,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--One day, the king said to these three,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.35,0:13:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Listen. Go find the tree that grows stars,\Nwhich is said to be in dragon's valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So BokeHontas,\NBokeBonboko and BokeBokepon
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.83,0:13:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--journeyed out, one to the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.03,0:13:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Once Grandpa starts that story,\N--journeyed out, one to the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.19,0:13:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Once Grandpa starts that story,\N--one to the mountain and one to the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--it'll take forever.\N--one to the mountain and one to the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.16,0:13:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm not gonna listen to all that.\N--one to the mountain and one to the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.63,0:13:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, the 317th King IngriMongri III's son
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, how long is this gonna go on?\N--IngriGrimori was quite a wise ruler.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Who knows.\N--IngriGrimori was quite a wise ruler.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had 18 children. His 18 children...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.64,0:14:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...He was a king who
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.98,0:14:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--carried out major reforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ahhh, I'm starving...\N--carried out major reforms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.65,0:14:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ahhh, I'm starving...\N--This King Ikemenes had so many children.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We won't be able to eat\N--This King Ikemenes had so many children.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--until this story is over, will we?\N--This King Ikemenes had so many children.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We won't be able to eat\N--He had many princes. 65 of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.92,0:14:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--the pork buns until then?\N--He had many princes. 65 of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.32,0:14:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Pork buns?\N--He had many princes. 65 of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear it was like, "If you throw a stone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.32,0:14:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy?\N--it'll hit one of the princes."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I gotta take a leak.\N--it'll hit one of the princes."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pork buns...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Grandpa Ryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.67,0:14:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming this way!\NWhat am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Don't come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pork buns smell yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.96,0:14:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't hit him yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:15:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh, pork buns...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.98,0:15:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, the 1,111th... no,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.38,0:15:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the 1,121st King was HokeHontas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, NemeNememitas
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.15,0:15:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, where're you going?\N--thought about what he could do
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.65,0:15:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm worried about Luffy\N--thought about what he could do
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.65,0:15:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--since he's gone for a long time.\N--to protect this kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.65,0:15:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--So I'll go check.\N--to protect this kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--So I'll go check.\N--Then, he made preparation
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.99,0:15:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's not fair.\N--Then, he made preparation
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.33,0:15:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nami-san's lovely\Neven when she sneaks out.\N--before large countries attacked them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.16,0:15:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phew! Good grief!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.33,0:15:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! Not even one bun is left!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.84,0:15:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this is yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.51,0:15:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yummy?! How do you intend to make\Nup for eating everyone's share?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.01,0:15:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.68,0:15:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.95,0:15:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What made this trail?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Dead end?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.96,0:15:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.63,0:16:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.63,0:16:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy, what're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.30,0:16:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--A hole.\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.00,0:16:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they went across here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.34,0:16:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.34,0:16:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suspension Bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.61,0:16:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the other side of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:17:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How far did they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.69,0:17:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.63,0:17:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I was fine.\NThese weird pirates saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.97,0:17:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they're not that scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.97,0:17:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be hungry. I brought\NGrandpa Bokuden's pork buns.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.47,0:17:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go. No! Slow down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.74,0:17:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry. I still don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I'm searching very hard,\NI still haven't found a clue yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.98,0:17:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who on earth Apis is talking to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Apis! Who're you talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.99,0:17:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just jump out and say "hey"!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.18,0:18:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Amazing! Amazing! Amazing!\N--Stop it! I said stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.62,0:18:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.62,0:18:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the real thing! Is he alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Leave him alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe... that it really exists...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.63,0:18:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that dragons were just legends!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is incredible!\NWhere did you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.98,0:18:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... You want to go home, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.82,0:18:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.99,0:18:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu says that you\Ncan be his friend, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.66,0:18:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says he can tell\Nyou're a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, how could you\Nread Grandpa Ryu's mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.17,0:18:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I somehow did.\N--Somehow...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.10,0:18:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.94,0:19:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be... a devil fruit...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.95,0:19:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have the power of\Na devil fruit, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I ate one called\NWhisper-Whisper Fruit or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since then, I've become\Nable to read animals' minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you knew\Na wind was coming that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. The seabirds told me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.63,0:19:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I met Grandpa Ryu thanks to\Nthe Whisper-Whisper Fruit, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.31,0:19:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard such\Na sad voice before...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:20:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! I'm coming to help you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.68,0:20:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it you who called me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had lost his energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said that he got separated\Nfrom his friends and
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.02,0:20:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that since then he had\Nbeen looking for Lost Island,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.75,0:20:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where the dragons' nest is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.69,0:20:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't Lost Island sink\Na long long time ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu says that the\Nisland will surface again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says it's about time,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.14,0:20:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he no longer clearly\Nremembers where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.37,0:20:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gotten very old\Nand lost the energy to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.04,0:20:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he keeps telling me\Nthat he wants to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna help, but I can't figure out\Nwhere such an island exists at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.32,0:20:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The legend by itself\Ndoesn't really give me a clue...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.99,0:20:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I asked the Navy who happened\Nto stop by this island about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:21:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a mistake.\NThey were looking for Dragonite.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.33,0:21:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dragonite... you mean\Nthe one for immortality?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.67,0:21:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They took you away\Nbecause of such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.67,0:21:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. They told me to tell them\Neverything I knew and took me away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.01,0:21:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pendant that I made with a claw
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.51,0:21:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu gave me may\Nhave been another reason, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you escaped in that storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.41,0:21:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You are too reckless!\N--I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.35,0:21:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I keep this a secret to\Nthe villagers and even to Bokuden-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.02,0:21:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to cause troubles for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.36,0:21:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want to take Grandpa Ryu back\Nto his home no matter what it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.69,0:21:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He always tells me that he'll\Nget his energy back for sure
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.36,0:21:33.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once he goes back to the dragons' nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.36,0:21:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find it for him no matter\Nhow many years it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.70,0:21:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For sure... No matter what it takes,\NI'll find it for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.04,0:21:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then! I'll take him there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.31,0:21:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Were you listening?!\NLost Island sank into the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.65,0:21:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since the legendary\NMillennial Dragon actually exists,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.65,0:21:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Lost Island\Nalso exists somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.42,0:21:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An island that's not even on a map?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.99,0:22:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's why we're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.66,0:22:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An island that's not even on a map, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.66,0:22:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what the heck? Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.33,0:22:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--All right!\N--Really?! Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.33,0:22:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah.\N--Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.00,0:22:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that that's been decided, eat more!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.00,0:22:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Luffy, I forgot to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.34,0:22:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa Ryu is a little senile.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.68,0:22:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl had a pendant with\Na Millennial Dragon's claw.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.02,0:22:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She must know about Lost Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.02,0:22:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That darn girl who knows\Nthe secret of the Dragonite...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.76,0:22:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely capture her this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.07,0:22:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My overflowing feelings don't connect
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as I firmly squeeze your hand back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.98,0:22:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set off by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:23:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so keep watching me intently\Nas I go into the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.76,0:23:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about it\Na bit since this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so hot?
